commit.message:
Delete all lines containing "$Revision:".

	* xeinfo.adb: Don't look for revision numbers.
	* xnmake.adb: Likewise.
	* xsinfo.adb: Likewise.
	* xsnames.adb: Likewise.
	* xtreeprs.adb: Likewise.

From-SVN: r50768
